-Ice+Applications&amp;rft.pub=Institute+of+Environmental+Physics%2C+University+of+Bremen&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.au=G.+Heygster&amp;rft.au=S.+Hendricks&amp;rft.au=L.+Kaleschke&amp;rft.au=N.+Maass&amp;rft.au=P.+Mills&amp;rft.au=D.+Stammer&amp;rft.au=R.+T.+Tonboe&amp;rft.au=C.+Haas&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASea+ice+thickness\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2257\nCached time: 20180918092803\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.108 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.146 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 347/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 9049/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 113/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 6052/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.054/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 2.48 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  127.347      1 -total\n 68.57%   87.325      1 Template:Reflist\n 35.95%   45.776      3 Template:Cite_web\n 22.79%   29.018      1 Template:See_also\n  6.37%    8.109      1 Template:Anchor\n  6.18%    7.873      1 Template:Cite_journal\n  5.65%    7.192      1 Template:Cite_techreport\n  4.19%    5.339      1 Template:Cite_news\n  2.35%    2.988      1 Template:Main_other\n  2.08%    2.653      1 Template:Column-width\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:28433988-0!canonical and timestamp 20180918092803 and revision id 860096109\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"Sea_ice"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Climate"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Remote_sensing"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Radiometry"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Climate_change_science"}],"links":[{"ns":0,"exists":"","*":"Alfred Wegener Institute fo